# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/).

***

## [0.1.0] - 2026-04-10

### Added
- `main.py` — CLI entry point using `--prompt` argument to query the database in natural language
- `config.py` — secure configuration module that loads all credentials from `.env`
- `.env.example` — environment variable template for Ollama and SQL Server settings
- `requirements.txt` — project dependencies
- `.gitignore` — excludes `.env` and generated files from version control
- `README.md` — setup, usage, configuration, and troubleshooting guide

### Architecture
- Gemma 3 (via Ollama) as the local LLM backend — no API key required
- LangChain `create_sql_agent` with `ZERO_SHOT_REACT_DESCRIPTION` agent type
- SQL Server connectivity via `mssql+pyodbc` and SQLAlchemy
- Support for both SQL Server Authentication and Windows Authentication
- All credentials isolated in `.env` — zero hardcoded values in source code
